      skos:prefLabel "Full Business Plan as Source of Truth" ;
      skos:note "Scarlet wants to get the full business plan draft done — which includes all fundraising pieces strung together. The fundraising briefs are audience-specific proxies; the business plan is the whole picture so that work happens on the actual plan, not through document proxies. Scarlet: 'Which is, you know, the whole aswritten philosophy.'" ;
